+//! Wire snapshots for the Gemini `generateContent` dialect. The model is
+//! part of the URL path, auth is the `x-goog-api-key` header, and the
+//! decoder mints synthetic UUID tool-call ids (normalized to `[UUID]` in
+//! these snapshots).
